    <scopecontent>
    <head>Descriptive Entry</head>
     <p>This accession consists of records maintained by Joanne M. Gernstein London, Curator, documenting the planning and design of exhibitions and events related to the Enola 
    Gay. Materials include correspondence, memoranda, draft scripts, notes, images, clippings, floor plans, an audiotape, a poster, and related materials.</p> </scopecontent> 
     
     
 
    
    
    
    
        
